data.description: This beautiful ranch style home has 3 bedrooms and two bathrooms on the main level and another full bathroom in the finished basement that could be turned into an apartment or mother in law suite. Basement also has a storm shelter that's re-enforced with cinderblocks and concrete. Located right down the road from Loretta Lynns house and well maintained. This home has custom feature walls, a nice open kitchen with plenty of cabinet and counter top space and lots of natural light. Backyard is fully fenced and feels private. Swing set and large shed convey with the home. Seller can close anytime!
